// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mtyyDR random domino tiling int, 2023 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlGcWR random domino square tiling int

// Tiling of randomly (horizontally/vertically) aligned domino tiles
// (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domino_tiling)
// Integer version (only final coloring float).
// Tiling function returns 2d tile indices which should be unique (but part of the indices are unused).

// tags: random, tiling, tesselation, domino

